                    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    <strong>Zurhu Expedition Adventures</strong> is a dynamic travel and tourism company based in Nairobi, Kenya. We specialize in road trips, private tours, adventure safaris, and customized travel packages across Kenya and East Africa. 
	Formerly known as Zuru Adventures, we rebranded to better reflect our expanded services and international ambitions. Our mission is to help you explore hidden gems, connect with nature, and create unforgettable memories.
	 Whether you're a solo traveler, a couple, family, or group, we have something tailored just for you.
	 We also organize charity events, themed hikes, and cultural experiences.Let's turn your wanderlust into reality with Zuru – where every trip is a new story!</p>


